SDIRK-3 LibTorch Interface for WRF
===================================

This directory contains the minimal SDIRK-3 stub implementation for WRF integration.

Directory Structure:
--------------------
libtorch_wrf/
├── Makefile          # Main makefile for building the library
├── lib/             
│   └── libsdirk3_libtorch.a  # Static library for WRF linking
└── sdirk3/
    ├── Makefile              # Subdirectory makefile
    ├── sdirk3_c_interface.h  # C interface header
    └── sdirk3_stub.cpp       # Stub implementation

Building:
---------
make        # Build the library
make clean  # Clean build artifacts

The library is automatically built during WRF compilation when using
configure option 37 (Darwin GNU/OpenMPI with SDIRK-3 LibTorch).

Integration:
------------
The library provides C-callable functions required by module_implicit_sdirk3.F:
- sdirk3_tile_solver_create
- sdirk3_tile_solver_destroy  
- sdirk3_tile_acoustic_step
- sdirk3_tile_rk_tendency

Note:
-----
This is a stub implementation. The actual SDIRK-3 mathematical implementation
has been developed and tested separately.